      "user_message": "I appreciate that. However, I specifically need the appointment to be *registered* for both of us, not just for me with him as an attendee. Our previous bank always did it that way. Is it absolutely not possible to book a single online meeting for \"Alex and [Husband's Name] Smith\" in your system?",
